# ReviewSite: Modern Professional UI/Theme Guidelines

## Color Palette

### Base Colors
- Primary Background: #121212 (Very dark gray)
- Secondary Background: #1E1E1E (Dark gray for cards/modals)
- Primary Text: #FFFFFF (Pure white)
- Secondary Text: #A0A0A0 (Muted gray)

### Accent Colors
- Primary Accent: #DC2626 (Professional Red)
- Primary Accent Hover: #B91C1C (Dark Red for hover/active)
- Highlight: #03A9F4 (Bright blue for focus/active)
- Success: #4CAF50 (Green)
- Warning: #FFC107 (Yellow)
- Error: #DC2626 (Same as primary accent)

### Borders
- Standard: #292929 (Subtle border gray)
- Highlight: #03A9F4 (Matches highlight accent)

## Typography

### Fonts
- **Primary (Headings):** Poppins
  - Regular (400)
  - Semi-bold (600)
  - Bold (700)
- **Secondary (Body Text):** Inter
  - Regular (400)
  - Semi-bold (600)
  - Bold (700)

Body size font in all areas should be a minimum of 16px.

## Components

### Common Classes
- Primary Button: `bg-[#DC2626] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#B91C1C] transition-colors`
- Secondary Button: `bg-[#1E1E1E] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-[#DC2626] hover:bg-[#232326] hover:border-[#B91C1C] transition-colors`
- Card: `bg-[#1E1E1E] rounded-lg shadow-md p-4`
- Form Input: `w-full rounded-lg border-[#292929] bg-[#18181B] p-2.5 text-white placeholder-[#A0A0A0] focus:border-[#03A9F4] focus:ring-[#03A9F4]`
- Form Select: `w-full rounded-lg border-[#292929] bg-[#18181B] p-2.5 text-white focus:border-[#03A9F4] focus:ring-[#03A9F4]`
- Form Textarea: `w-full rounded-lg border-[#292929] bg-[#18181B] p-2.5 pl-4 text-white placeholder-[#A0A0A0] focus:border-[#03A9F4] focus:ring-[#03A9F4]`
- Form Checkbox: `bg-[#1E1E1E] border-[#292929] text-[#DC2626] rounded focus:ring-[#DC2626] focus:ring-offset-[#1E1E1E]`
- Modal: `bg-[#1E1E1E] rounded-lg p-6 max-w-md w-full mx-4`

### Action Bar
- edit: Pencil icon, blue hover (`hover:bg-[#03A9F4]/20`)
- view: Book icon, gray hover (`hover:bg-[#A0A0A0]/20`)
- remove / delete: Trash icon, red hover (`hover:bg-[#DC2626]/20`)
- add: Plus icon, green hover (`hover:bg-[#4CAF50]/20`)

## Spacing & Layout
- Use multiples of 4px for spacing (e.g., p-4, m-4, gap-4)
- Cards and containers: `p-4` or `p-6` for padding
- Section backgrounds: alternate between #121212 and #1E1E1E for contrast

## Accessibility
- Focus states: 2px solid #03A9F4 outline, 2px outline offset
- Minimum contrast ratio: 4.5:1
- Interactive elements: minimum 44x44px, clear hover/active states, keyboard navigation support

## Animation
- Standard: 0.2s ease-in-out
- Hover transform: translateY(-2px)
- Loading state: use animate-pulse

## Icons
- Use SVG icons, consistent sizing (24x24px), aria-labels
- Social icons: neutral by default, red on hover

